<h2 id="personal">Personal</h2>
<p>I am a Tokyo-based Linux enthusiast, programmer, husband, and father. I run <a href="http://www.gentoo.org/">Gentoo Linux</a> with <a href="http://icculus.org/openbox/">openbox</a>, and do all of my coding in <a href="http://www.xemacs.org/">XEmacs</a>.</p>
<h2 id="tlug">TLUG</h2>
<p>I have been a member of <a href="http://www.tlug.jp/">TLUG</a> since late 2000, and currently serve as Listmaster.</p>
